content: waste game

After a first try, I am really impressed. The graphics is outstanding. One can play both Chess and Xiang Qi as well as Go (which for the moment I did not try). It is possible to choose several styles of pieces. The traditional ones are gorgeous; the phantasy sets are also outstanding, but I would have liked to have one without flames (it is just my taste and not so important). A possible improvement could maybe be an option to use external engines. All in all, highly recommended.
